rows.label: qst001103_msg001
rows.name:
Brought the stuff, did you? I'll get the
finishing touches done lickety-split!

rows.label: qst001103_msg002
rows.name: Hmmm...

rows.label: qst001103_msg003
rows.name:
Now, let me think. What was it
I was going to make again...?

rows.label: qst001103_msg004
rows.name:
Yeah, hmm...
I feel like I sort of remember...
But then again, I sort of don't...

rows.label: qst001103_msg005
rows.name: You remember, don't you?

rows.label: qst001103_msg006
rows.name: What was Silvio trying to make?

rows.label: qst001103_msg007
rows.name: 体力があがるアクセサリーの名称を入れる（仮）

rows.label: qst001103_msg008
rows.name: 素早くなるアクセサリーの名称を入れる（仮）

rows.label: qst001103_msg009
rows.name:
Ah! Of course.
Yes, I remember perfectly now.

rows.label: qst001103_msg010
rows.name: OK! I'm good to go! Leave it to me!

rows.label: qst001103_msg011
rows.name: Hmmm... Was that really it...?

rows.label: qst001103_msg012
rows.name:
Now that you say it, it does
sort of ring a bell...?

rows.label: qst001103_msg013
rows.name:
Ah, whatever.
You just leave it to me.

rows.label: qst001103_msg014
rows.name:
Done and dusted! That's my
masterpiece, that is!

rows.label: qst001103_msg015
rows.name:
It was all thanks to you lot that
I managed to get this made!

rows.label: qst001103_msg016
rows.name:
Well, you should have this, as a token
of thanks.

rows.label: qst001103_msg017
rows.name:
Nah, no need to thank me. I haven't
had this much fun putting something
together since...well, I can't remember...

rows.label: qst001103_msg018
rows.name:
Hey, when we first met, didn't you say
that you'd make any accessory we
asked for?

rows.label: qst001103_msg019
rows.name:
By the way...when we first met, didn't
you say you'd make any accessory
we named, hmm?

rows.label: qst001103_msg020
rows.name:
Oh, yes! When we first meet,
did friend not offer to making
whatever accessories we like?

rows.label: qst001103_msg021
rows.name:
By the by, didn't you offer to make us
more accessories when we first met?
I seem to remember you saying that.

rows.label: qst001103_msg022
rows.name:
Hey, by the way, you said before
you'd be able to knock up any wacky
accessory we dreamed up, didn't you?

rows.label: qst001103_msg023
rows.name:
Erm... Did I? I dunno. Maybe I did.
I can't remember.

rows.label: qst001103_msg024
rows.name:
But, one thing's for sure! I'm going to
keep making whatever takes my fancy!
